name: "It's okay" by Cinthia Ponce
description:
It's okay, I just have to get through this.


I can get some rest, after I've fallen.
I'm doing well, when I have a hard time like this I'll quit and then I'll come back stronger. 

I'll just endure a little hardship
And I'll say to myself: 
You're doing great
You're doing great
You have to take your time, you can do it.
